      "weather": "FINE",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LEGENDS TOLD (2) broke well and quickly mustered speed to win over the 407m at this track two runs back then settled forward again when finishing second at this track last start. The form out of last race has been strong. Can go on with it. ASTON HAYES (7) was below best at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth at this track, but was among the placings at this track three back. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. RUPEE RANGER (3) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 24.18 beating Sunburnt Dawn. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Can measure up again. JESTER BEACH (1) is worth consideration after filling a hole last start.",
